BT /Helvetica 8 Tf 0.350 0.350 0.350 rg 54.00 738.00 Td (FPGA AI Suite 2026.1.1 Installation Guide) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 720.00 Td (Run:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 697.50 Td (python3 -c "import openvino; print\(openvino.__version__\)") Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 686.88 Td (echo $COREDLA_ROOT) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 676.25 Td (dla_compiler --version) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 665.62 Td (quartus_pgm --version) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 655.00 Td (jtagconfig) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 634.38 Td (Expected OpenVINO version begins with:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 611.88 Td (2025.4) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 591.25 Td (If no FPGA board is connected, jtagconfig may show:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 568.75 Td (No JTAG hardware available) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 548.12 Td (That is normal.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 18 Tf 0.050 0.180 0.350 rg 54.00 509.62 Td (Part B - Linux/Ubuntu Docker installation flow) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 475.12 Td (B1. Recommended for Ubuntu 26.04) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 449.62 Td (Ubuntu 26.04 is not officially listed as a native FPGA AI Suite target. Use Docker.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 425.12 Td (B2. Install Docker Engine) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 397.62 Td (sudo apt update) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 387.00 Td (sudo apt install -y ca-certificates curl gnupg) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 376.38 Td (sudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 365.75 Td (curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 355.12 Td (  o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 344.50 Td (sudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 323.88 Td (If Docker has a repo for your Ubuntu codename, use it. If not, use the Ubuntu 24.04 noble repo:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 301.38 Td (echo "deb [arch=$\(dpkg --print-architecture\) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docke) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 290.75 Td (  r.gpg] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu noble stable" | sudo tee /etc/) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 280.12 Td (  apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 259.50 Td (Install Docker:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 237.00 Td (sudo apt update) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 226.38 Td (sudo apt install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 215.75 Td (   docker-compose-plugin) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 205.12 Td (sudo systemctl enable docker) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 194.50 Td (sudo systemctl start docker) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 183.88 Td (sudo usermod -aG docker $USER) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 163.25 Td (Log out and log back in. Test:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 140.75 Td (docker run hello-world) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 116.12 Td (B3. Pull complete FPGA AI Suite image) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 88.62 Td (docker pull alterafpga/fpgaaisuite:2026.1.1-quartus) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 8 Tf 0.4 0.4 0.4 rg 286.00 28 Td (Page 3 of 10) Tj ET
